node.text:
For 180 years, The Dalmore has been created by an unbroken chain of visionary whisky makers renowned for their exceptional whisky making. Thanks to them, the distillery is home to some of the rarest and most precious single malt in Scotland.

Today their restless pursuit for excellence will see their mastery presented as part of a celebration of truly unique masterpieces at @sothebys. 
The Dalmore 1973, Cask No. 8 is now on offer at IN CONFIDENCE: SELECTED MASTERPIECES, open for bidding from now until 23 May. #dalmorewhisky #dalmore #sothebys @sothebyswine

node.title: The Dalmore | IN CONFIDENCE: SELECTED MASTERPIECES at Sotheby’s

node.text:
Majestic and refined with a unique Port finish. The Dalmore Port Wood Reserve is perfect for sharing on warm summer days. 

#dalmore #dalmorewhisky

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Dalmore on June 24, 2021. May be an image of drink and indoor.

node.text:
Soak up the sun and tickle your taste buds with the intricate aromas of citrus fruits, chocolate and aromatic spices.

The Dalmore 12 Year Old is a whisky with character beyond its years. Drink it on its own or serve mixed.

#dalmore #dalmorewhisky

#dalmore #dalmorewhisky
